持 33.39 万股，而雪佛龙和动视暴雪均被减持，不过整体规模仍位居前十。 伯克希尔 Q4 并未新建或清仓股票，减持了 8 个标的，并增持了 3 个标的。伯克希尔增持的三只股票分别是苹果、派拉蒙以及美国建筑产品制造商路易斯安那太平洋公司。减持的八只股票中，雪佛龙和动视暴雪位列前二，但减持比例不算太大，而台积电和美国合众银行的减持比例分别高达 86% 和 91%。巴菲特砍仓 86%，台湾「股王」大跌！「股神」最新操作曝光：加仓这只美股巨头 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-7857cde62f89ef38736db4ad146f912d_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "65 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/584150800"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7pmH5NCBk6dMEAMaCDkyMDkzMTgwIPeLsZ8GMAU4xQFAFnIJNTg0MTUwODAweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1676600467.5471432", "card_id": "Q_583264109", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 133}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有什么蔬菜适合烧烤？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-246626edd5b982c21a0f6a9b06668e99_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/583264109"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7pmH5NCBk6dMEAMaCDkxODk1OTYxIKX8mJ8GMAA4hgFAF3IJNTgzMjY0MTA5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1676600467.547606", "card_id": "Q_575001389", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 535}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你认为学历和手艺，哪样能让你生活的更好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "参赛问题"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"